WEBVTT

00:00:58.069 --> 00:01:01.100
orqali yengib o'tadilar.
Qanchalar g'ayrioddiy tuyulmasin,

00:01:01.100 --> 00:01:04.728
imildoqlar suvsiz yashay oladigan 
yagona mavjudot emas.

00:01:04.728 --> 00:01:05.780
Bakteriyalar, arxaeya

00:01:05.780 --> 00:01:08.309
deb ataluvchi bir hujayrali organizmlar,

00:01:08.309 --> 00:01:09.090
o'simliklar,

00:01:09.090 --> 00:01:13.269
hatto ayrim jonzotlar ham butunlay qurib
qolishiga qaramay, omon qolishlari mumkin.

00:01:13.269 --> 00:01:14.671
Aksariyat imildoqlar buning

00:01:14.671 --> 00:01:18.571
uchun "bochkacha holati" ga 
o'tishlari kerak bo'ladi.

00:01:18.571 --> 00:01:20.030
Ular shar shaklida buralib,

00:01:20.030 --> 00:01:23.620
boshi hamda sakkiz oyog'ini 
ichkariga tortib oladilar va

00:01:23.620 --> 00:01:27.000
suv kelishini kutadilar.

00:01:27.000 --> 00:01:29.141
Suv tanqis bo'lib, imildoqlar angidribioz

00:01:29.141 --> 00:01:31.501
holatiga kirganida 
maxsus molekulalarni